TI  - Community eco-tourism in rural Peru: Resilience and adaptive capacities to the Covid-19 pandemic and climate change
T2  - JOURNAL OF HOSPITALITY AND TOURISM MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - COVID-19
KW  - Community resilience
KW  - Sustainability
