TI  - Social protection for transformative resilience: do programmes really address underlying causes of vulnerability of subsistence farmers to climate change?
T2  - LOCAL ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Bangladesh
KW  - social protection
KW  - subjectivity
KW  - resilience
KW  - transformative
