TI  - The interactive effects of rainfall, temperature and water level on fish yield in Lake Bangweulu fishery, Zambia
T2  - JOURNAL OF THERMAL BIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Fishery
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Climate change
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
