TI  - Limiting global warming to 2 °C benefits building climate resilience in rice-wheat systems in India through crop calendar management
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate resilience
KW  - Rice-wheat system
