TI  - Recent intensification of the seasonal rainfall cycle in equatorial Africa revealed by farmer perceptions, satellite-based estimates, and ground-based station measurements
T2  - CLIMATIC CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - MAIZE PRODUCTION
