TI  - Climate change perspectives of coffee farmers in Junín Mountain tropical forests and CMIP5 projections
T2  - FRONTIERS IN CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - adaptation
KW  - climate models
KW  - coffee
KW  - local knowledge
