TI  - Enhancing Livelihood Resilience Through Specialty Agriculture: A Study of Daylily Farmers in Northern China's Agro-Pastoral Ecotone
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - agro-pastoral ecotone
KW  - daylily
KW  - livelihood resilience
