TI  - Agro-pastoral conflicts in Benin: when policies fall short
T2  - REVIEW OF SOCIAL ECONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - Agro-pastoralism
KW  - conflict
KW  - politico-institutional
KW  - PASTORALISM
