TI  - Determinants of climate adaptation strategies by smallholder coffee growers in Southwestern Ethiopia
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Coffee
KW  - Multivariate probit
KW  - Southwestern Ethiopia
KW  - ADOPTION
KW  - VARIABILITY
