TI  - Living and Responding to Climatic Stresses: Perspectives from Smallholder Farmers in Hanang' District, Tanzania
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Climatic stresses
KW  - Rainfall variability
KW  - Perception
KW  - Incremental adaptation
