TI  - Climate change and agriculture nexus in Bangladesh: Evidence from ARDL and ECM techniques
T2  - PLOS CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - ECONOMIC-GROWTH
KW  - CO2 EMISSIONS
KW  - TIME-SERIES
KW  - COINTEGRATION
