TI  - Do farmers' perceptions and socio-economic factors drive cocoa agroforestry and sustainable soil carbon management practices in West Africa?
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Soil organic carbon
KW  - Agroforestry
KW  - Sustainable cocoa farming
KW  - Climate change and cocoa farmers
KW  - Africa
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
