TI  - Evaluation of agroecological processes implemented in olive production systems: an analysis in Boyacá, Colombia
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - climate change adaptation
KW  - food systems resilience
KW  - sustainable agriculture
KW  - multidimensional
