TI  - The effect of the silvopastoral system on milk production and reproductive performance of dairy cows and its contribution to adaptation to a changing climate in the drylands of Benin (West-Africa)
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - dairy cattle
