TI  - Consistency in climate change impact reports among indigenous peoples and local communities depends on site contexts
T2  - NPJ CLIMATE ACTION
LA  - English
KW  - SCIENTIFIC-KNOWLEDGE
KW  - PERCEPTIONS
KW  - ADAPTATION
