TI  - "Climate-smart agriculture and food security: Cross-country evidence from West Africa"
T2  - GLOBAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE-HUMAN AND POLICY DIMENSIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Adoption
KW  - Yields
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate-smart agriculture
