TI  - Measuring livelihood resilience and its determinants among smallholder farmers facing climate change in the Sidaama region of Ethiopia using beta regression
T2  - DISCOVER SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Absorptive capacity
KW  - Adaptive capacity
KW  - Beta regression
KW  - Livelihood resilience
