TI  - Unequal resilience: adaptive strategies among smallholder farmers in Indonesia
T2  - DEVELOPMENT IN PRACTICE
LA  - English
KW  - Double squeeze
KW  - adaptive strategies
KW  - policy access
KW  - smallholder farmers
KW  - resilience pathways
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
