TI  - Assessing farmers' vulnerability to floods and landslides in Kerala using a multidimensional Societal Vulnerability Index (SVIFL)
T2  - DISCOVER ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Floods
KW  - Landslides
KW  - Farmers
KW  - Vulnerability assessment
