TI  - Remoteness and its impact on productivity growth among Malawi's smallholder household farmers: A Malmquist and tobit regression approach
T2  - AFRICAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL AND RESOURCE ECONOMICS-AFJARE
LA  - English
KW  - Malmquist DEA
KW  - productivity remoteness
KW  - technical change
