TI  - Rooted in crisis, growing solutions: economic impacts and adaptive pathways for Fiji's climate-threatened sugarcane industry
T2  - FRONTIERS IN CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - sugarcane (Saccharum officinarum)
KW  - climate hazards
KW  - farmer vulnerability
KW  - agricultural adaptation
KW  - climate resilience
