TI  - The role of integrated prawn farming in climate change adaptation in Bangladesh: ecosystem services, economic viability and barriers
T2  - JOURNAL OF FISHERIES
LA  - English
KW  - adaptation
KW  - climatic hazards
KW  - economic suitability
KW  - ecosystem services
KW  - integrated prawn farming
