TI  - The poverty implications of climate-induced crop yield changes by 2030
T2  - GLOBAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE-HUMAN AND POLICY DIMENSIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Vulnerability
KW  - Agriculture
KW  - Food security
KW  - Hunger
