TI  - To cope or to sustain? Eroding long-term sustainability in an Indonesian coral reef fishery
T2  - REGIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptive capacity
KW  - Coping strategies
KW  - Indonesia
KW  - Precious corals
KW  - Sea cucumbers
